def is_even(s: str, n: int) -> bool:
    parts = s.split('.')
    fractional_part = parts[1]
    fractional_part = fractional_part.rstrip('0')
    if not fractional_part:
        return int(parts[0]) % 2 == 0
    return int(fractional_part) % 2 != 0
